msgid ""
"Since ``**`` has higher precedence than ``-``, ``-3**2`` will be interpreted "
"as ``-(3**2)`` and thus result in ``-9``.  To avoid this and get ``9``, you "
"can use ``(-3)**2``."
msgstr ""
